<scene_requirements>
Design ONE comic panel featuring Vita that:
- Shows her engaging with the article's specific health topic
- Uses a setting appropriate to the topic (lab for research, kitchen for nutrition, gym for fitness, bedroom for sleep, park for outdoor activity)
- Includes 2-3 props relevant to the topic
- Has a text bubble with the single most actionable or surprising fact from the article (in Ukrainian)
- Specifies color palette that matches the mood (energetic = warm golds and greens, calming = cool blues and sage, scientific = clean whites and teals)

IMPORTANT: The scene description must be detailed enough for an image generation model to produce a consistent result.
Describe Vita's physical appearance in every scene — do not assume the image model remembers her.
</scene_requirements>
